s/2025-09/ba7819a0-8cf3-11f0-bffd-14e2c22f9468" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OY8dzQ6BEWcqNCSs8Vrx7Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/ba7819a0-8cf3-11f0-bffd-14e2c22f9468" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/961b5e/f/800x0/https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OY8dzQ6BEWcqNCSs8Vrx7Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https%3A//s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/ba7819a0-8cf3-11f0-bffd-14e2c22f9468"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #999; "&gt;夜繽紛變夜蕭條，財赤下「賽馬經濟」成庫房支柱？圖為快活谷馬場資料圖片。(Photo by Lo Chun Kit /Getty Images)·Lo Chun Kit via Getty Images&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[url=https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_[%E2%80%A6]ub2=HK_YMktg&amp;amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;amp;uuid=s1kW4IOA4iZoKC480912&amp;amp;uuid=n71xwVw3nRy25ecw0845&amp;amp;uuid=cSM0RfGjBMAB6hoF0568&amp;amp;uuid=DuIuMOWACtzsBO9v0182&amp;amp;uuid=xB4uJWWz1ECOpprK0310&amp;amp;uuid=tI3bFLm2SkvtQBBV0990&amp;amp;uuid=fxfksXClqFqTK6wd0763&amp;amp;uuid=ybkNYokd68f51swq0786&amp;amp;uuid=FMZsYcaovPDiRiEn0238&amp;amp;uuid=DBJmJP7M8dIuFAza1268&amp;amp;uuid=UfT13nXCr4cvW6En0657&amp;amp;uuid=PXZAVgzDtTubfzB50492&amp;amp;uuid=vKvKMdPxcax8uKVB0858&amp;amp;uuid=b9lwBa9QJpW1nDGE0691&amp;amp;uuid=vlRWlWNhKBZhiAgc0737&amp;amp;uuid=uYLODeNHhsonQhC20339&amp;amp;uuid=pifNpXs63jptqi5H0279&amp;amp;uuid=qp3YUzwMSdJD6vlL0645&amp;amp;uuid=rSYcc3skG3GLP5390333&amp;amp;uuid=1R5wK6mBCx7lpBL30982&amp;amp;uuid=uv2JhhemlLAEcqZS0245&amp;amp;uuid=HPOVGtqDrX1VPYoP0134&amp;amp;uuid=Vbm9qeF23UbKFUwV0740&amp;amp;uuid=Vo0ggtFtaaFjlbAR0293&amp;amp;uuid=Ahrs29aW8UxKfVmp0319&amp;amp;uuid=KY0FM5IlGv5VyL3b0194&amp;amp;uuid=soNUUI0W39s6NWaQ0319&amp;amp;uuid=fF9FZQ3iPNdsnDWO0733&amp;amp;uuid=NOj3FXU9Tx70uoXQ0820&amp;amp;uuid=MhCeryurfIarguZ70925&amp;amp;uuid=dJI9g1zfikEQ3MMB0696&amp;amp;uuid=MoePYhrruAkd1rRs0006&amp;amp;uuid=3uloGdI2IxSVhxco0690&amp;amp;uuid=0g1fhWirY5eHWOo00348&amp;amp;uuid=pB3zJNo2pNKJnGDT0310&amp;amp;uuid=5uff9nLVdntja92R0991&amp;amp;uuid=lVoURqEo4b225m8c0686&amp;amp;uuid=r1VKOeN31MjW7xI90753&amp;amp;uuid=q0kOLvuspTV2UEMx0255&amp;amp;uuid=Lz5GIZHDJSDguZTU0988&amp;amp;uuid=8KB2pkDP7CtTJEfn0031&amp;amp;uuid=e0jKA61WpqkKrpy20289&amp;amp;uuid=M5Bw1vIAZqmSrjxV0292&amp;amp;uuid=SLaEgDglJvf5GRMv0638&amp;amp;uuid=d7EEH4xTRhgNOlXW0638]下載Yahoo財經APP[/url]&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.5rem"&gt;夜繽紛後勁不繼 吸引力弱&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;政府當年推廣「夜繽紛」時聲勢浩大，當局更聲稱部分商戶生意上升「幾成甚至一倍」，然而，當被追問經濟效益時，財經司副司長黃偉綸竟回應「沒有特別估算」，令人質疑政策依據。&lt;br/&gt;不過商戶的親身感受最實際，夜繽紛政策2023年9月推出，當中以12月開鑼的「廟街夜繽紛」為重頭戲，首四個月錄得120萬人次到訪，大收旺場，政府更添食舉行至翌年12月；然而新鮮感一過，暑假檔期卻乏人問津，當時有小食攤販大嘆最差時候整晚只有200多元生意。&lt;br/&gt;香港科大在夜繽紛推行數月後公布研究，指「夜繽紛」在內地社交平台的直接討論比例長期不足 1%，關注度遠低於「國慶煙花」、「迪士尼萬聖節」等景點級活動。香港民意研究所 2024 年調查更顯示，市民對夜繽紛印象雖深，但常見關鍵詞卻是「浪費、效率低、組織不善」，認為對本地經濟推動有限。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p align="center"&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573919220" original-img="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nWRVvAfS4l4HtMcby8ct6A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-12/aa9b8b90-9eaf-11ee-bf63-0e03b28a0b7a" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nWRVvAfS4l4HtMcby8ct6A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-12/aa9b8b90-9eaf-11ee-bf63-0e03b28a0b7a" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/1b7bee/f/800x0/https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nWRVvAfS4l4HtMcby8ct6A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https%3A//s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-12/aa9b8b90-9eaf-11ee-bf63-0e03b28a0b7a"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #999; "&gt;夜繽紛政策2023年9月推出，當中以12月開鑼的「廟街夜繽紛」為重頭戲。 (Photo by Vernon Yuen/NurPhoto via Getty Images)·NurPhoto via Getty Images&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align="center"&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573919220" original-img="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dca_visgt2H5ZMZegI_mUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-03/5b2ccc10-f64a-11ef-bfdf-21a4e329013d" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dca_visgt2H5ZMZegI_mUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-03/5b2ccc10-f64a-11ef-bfdf-21a4e329013d" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/d2d259/f/800x0/https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dca_visgt2H5ZMZegI_mUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https%3A//s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-03/5b2ccc10-f64a-11ef-bfdf-21a4e329013d"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #999; "&gt;對於向馬會徵收額外足球博彩稅，財政司陳茂波著馬會「佢自己諗掂佢啦」。 (Photo by Vernon Yuen/NurPhoto via Getty Images)·NurPhoto via Getty Images&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32029144&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=202835607268c0568edc1198_04103382"/><published>2025-09-09T23:02:56+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f658cccff5e3a7fa8a768f4fc3d4513b</id><title>仲使上台綁一年</title><updated>2025-09-09T23:04:48+08:00</updated><author><name>奇幻的pizza</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-09-09T23:04:48+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573919243"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573919243"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yaho